<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2188] Group ICVs waiting on row lock</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2188</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In the same spirit as group commit down in HLog, incrementColumnValue should be grouping all requests waiting on the row lock into one in HRegion. This means that 10 clients waiting on the lock should be all summed up and then applied only once.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12455561">HBASE-2188</key>
            <summary>Group ICVs waiting on row lock</summary>
